title: Monarch of Death
alternative_titles: Carnac the King of Dead Spirits
summary: Monarch of Death Manhwa 사령왕 카르나크 | Death King Karnak | Carnac the King of Dead Spirits | The King of Dead Souls I was a being that ruled over death. It took me a hundred years to come to a realization. A human should live a human life. One shouldn’t rule over something like that.
